00:48:57.204 --> 00:48:59.520
' And then there's a prayer.

00:48:59.520 --> 00:49:02.880
Do you want me to?

00:49:02.880 --> 00:49:03.858
Yeah, go ahead.

00:49:05.440 --> 00:49:05.620
I love it all.

00:49:05.620 --> 00:49:10.440
