00:49:11.263 --> 00:49:14.280
It says, 'Heavenly Father, thank you for Thy precious Holy Word.

00:49:14.280 --> 00:49:21.916
Thank you for the blood—redeemed not with corruptible things such as silver or gold but by the blood of the Lamb of God, Jesus.

00:49:21.916 --> 00:49:27.240
Thank you, Heavenly Father, for the fellowship we have with you.

00:49:27.240 --> 00:49:32.375
We have fellowship with the Father, with the Son, and with the Holy Spirit.

00:49:32.375 --> 00:49:40.880
We have fellowship one with another because we're walking in the light and the blood of Jesus Christ cleanses us from all sin.

00:49:40.880 --> 00:49:43.200
' I'm clean.

00:49:43.200 --> 00:49:46.720
I'm clean.

00:49:46.720 --> 00:49:58.400
I'm clean because the blood of Jesus Christ has made me clean.

00:50:01.855 --> 00:50:02.170
